This package includes utilities to manipulate Open Ephys Continuous files

usage: merge_continuous.py [-h] [-x] [-d DATA_DIR] channel [channel ...]

Merge OpenEphys Continuous files the timestamps are concatenated

positional arguments:
  channel      channels to be be merged

optional arguments:
  -h, --help   show this help message and exit
  -x           replace existing merge file
  -d DATA_DIR  folder where data reside
  -a           do AUX files instead of CH files
REVISION HISTORY

0.2: now processes AUX files too